  <features>
    <feature>A very simple yet deep mechanic : piling!</feature>
    <feature>An adventure you can play from one to four players!</feature>
    <feature>A drop in / drop out feature allowing players to join and leave at any time thanks a dynamic challenge rescalling!</feature>
    <feature>3 compelling worlds to explore and secrets to unravel!</feature>
	<feature>A lot of cute box-animals to meet and help throughout your journey!</feature>
	<feature>5 box-items to try out and experiment with!</feature>
	<feature>Even more toys to unlock and have fun with! </feature>
	<feature>More than 10 playable skins to customize your boxlings!</feature>
	<feature>6 mini-games for endless coopetitive fun with your friends!</feature>
	<feature>An art direction entirely revolving around cardboard, from textures to sound design!</feature>
	<feature>A strong focus on accessibility and usability!</feature>
  </features>

